This is a beta release of Umoria 5.2.  Please send bug reports to
wilson@ernie.berkeley.EDU or to the USENET newsgroup rec.games.moria.

Please read the file doc/FEATURES.NEW.  In particular, note the new commands
'G' for learning spells, and '=' for setting options.  Also, to attack
invisible creatures in walls, you must tunnel.
